data.name: Honey Mustard Dip
data.quickTastyDescription: A sweet and tangy dip perfect for veggies, pretzels, or chicken nuggets!
detailedCookingInstructions: In a medium bowl, combine honey, mustard, and mayonnaise.
Mix well until all ingredients are thoroughly combined.
Taste and adjust the mustard or honey according to your preference.
Serve immediately or refrigerate for later use.
